Name: Nike Air Zoom Hyperace
Short description: Technical and lightweight indoor shoe with perfect damping.
Description:
Product Description

Nike Air Zoom Hyperace 2 Men

The Nike Air Zoom Hyperace 2 is a technical and lightweight indoor shoe with perfect damping. By using the right colors combined with the Nike logo, this shoe has a sharp and sporty appearance. Features and benefits - TPU heelcounter provides enough comfort and firmness - Made with small, self-breathing holes that keep your feet cool, dry and active - The forefoot has some sort of airbag that gives an even better feeling while turning or moving quickly - The back of the shoe fits sporty to the heel and won't let you slide Color: White / Black SKU: AR5281-101

Name: MC David Tennis Elbow Strap
Description: MC David Tennis Elbow Strap Applies pressure over tendons to help relieve painful tennis elbow problems. Adjustable thermal neoprene wraparound support in convenient universal size features Velcro cinch strap and nylon facing on both sides. Available sizes: One size Color: SKU: 486R

Name: Victor Vibrastop

Name: Stanno Elite Sock Unisex
Description:
Stanno Elite Sock Unisex

The high-quality Marfil Shingo yarns in the footbed ensure a good transport of the bodily fluids and give a comfortable feeling. The stocking is ideal for indoor sports and tennis. Color: Black SKU: 442103-8000

Name: Hummel Spirit Training Set Women
Description:
Hummel Spirit Training Set Women

The Spirit training set by Hummel is made of soft polyester and the ClimaTec finish makes this training set sweat-proof. The comfortable fabric and sporty fit are an ideal combination during your practice. The shirt has a stylish, geometric print on the front and contains contrasting panels on the shoulders and arms. Name: Salming Diamond Game Shirt Women
Description:
Salming Diamond Game Shirt Women

Salming Diamond tee is made in a flexibel and functional Coolfeel fabric. The female fit and sober design with embossed raglansleeves will make you feel and look like a winner in every match. Features and benefits - Fit: Regular - Fabric: 100% Polyester Color: Black SKU: 1198736-0101

Name: Jako Leisure Jacket Performance Ladies
Description:
Jako Leisure Jacket Performance Ladies

The leisure jacket of the Jako Performance line is fully equipped with features. The zipper garage protects your chin. The mesh lining ensures good ventilation and the side pockets with zipper ensure that you do not lose anything. Thin microfibers transport the perspiration immediately to the outside. As a result, the material dries very quickly, protects against the cold and gives a pleasant body feeling during exercise. Features and benefits - Quick drying material - Zipper garage - Side pockets with zipper closure Color: Blue / White / Navy SKU: 9897-49

Name: Blindsave Goalie Gloves
Description:
Blindsave Goalie Gloves

Blindsave offers an absolutely new type of gloves: Light, breathable and with a specially covered sticky surface technology from American football. These gloves will help goalies to show their best performance in the goal. The palm side of the glove is made from a thin - rubber based - fabric that guarantees a perfect control of the ball. In the same time, this innovative fabric surface is thick enough to keep your hands safe, even from the toughest shots. The stretch lycra fabric covers the backhand side of the glove and is excellent material to ensure a perfect fit and comfort. It is very breathable from both sides to keep you cool and avoid hands from sweating. Features and benefits - Sticky surface technology - Breathable & Comfortable - Provides the best protection Color: Grey SKU: GGG18-XS

Name: Tunturi Bottle Rack
Description:
Tunturi Bottle Rack

Drinking during exercise The Tunturi foldable bottle rack is an easy bottle rack that can be used during team sports. With the bottle rack it is easy to take 8 bottles with you in one go. Ideal for football, volleyball or handball training. Because the rack is foldable, it can easily be taken along. Water bottles in the photo are not included, these can be ordered separately Color: SKU: 14TUSTE103

Name: Tunturi Referee Cards Set
Description:
Tunturi Referee Cards Set

Hand out cards during football The Tunturi referee card set is the set that can be used by all referees. With 2 bright cards, yellow and red, it will always be clearly visible which card will be dealt. The referee card set comes with a storage case and a pencil. Color: SKU: 14TUSTE140

Description:
Hummel Aarhus Short Women

This short for women from the Hummel Aarhus collection is made of 100% polyester with ClimaTex finish. The fast drying stretch-material provides the optimal movement freedom, while the sport shorts always fits thanks to the elastic waistband with pulling cord. Features and benefits - Feminine fit - Without inner pants - Regular fit - Material: 100% polyester Color: Black SKU: 120605-8000

Name: Errea Bolton Short Men
Description:
Errea Bolton Short Men

Errea Bolton Short Men Unisex sports shorts (for boys and girls). Cut and sewn with a contrasting vertical inlaid on the sides. Elasticated waistband with draw strings. Normal fit. Suitable for any sport. Breathable. Available in a wide range of colours. Just like the Bolton jersey, these sports shorts for boys and girls by Erreà are suitable for any sports activity. They are, however, particularly suitable for football and volleyball and are appreciated worldwide by top athletes. Their soft, lightweight and breathable fabric wicks sweat away and gives you a feeling of freshness at all times. The side vertical contrasting inlaid can be customised and allows you to match the pants with your team colours. Color: Blue / White SKU: D196-150

Name: Errea Knik Arm Sleeves
Description:
Errea Knik Arm Sleeves

Errea Knik Arm Warmer Errea Arm sleeves Inspired by the NBA world, these arm warmers by Erreà are perfect for athletes who practice sport regularly and want to protect their joints both while training and during competitions. Especially appreciated in the running world, these arm warmers have been developed to protect elbow joints: they fit around your body perfectly, and they are very lightweight and thin. Their muscle-compressive reticular skeleton provides comfort without constraints. Also in this garment characterized by an athletic look, the knitted tubular fabric technology reduces seams to a minimum, providing comfort, breathability and ergonomic fitting. Color: Red SKU: U655-02
